Introduction

Up To You was a South Korean project girl group formed through Afreeca TV's reality survival show series "U2U: Up To You". The group line-ups are not permanent and they separate after the release of one digital single each season.

The first season's Top 5 winners made the group's initiating debut on January 17, 2023, with the digital single, "Super Star". The line-up consisted of Youya (Rank 1), Gyumdong (Rank 3), Yoon Suya (Rank 5), Nayomi (Rank 2), and Kim Rayul (Rank 4).

The second season's Top 5 winners released the group's second digital single on August 4, 2023, with "Crush On You". The line-up consisted of Acare (Rank 1), Dada (Rank 2), Lee Hamin (Rank 4), Kim Sooyeoung (Rank 5), and I'm Suho (Rank 3).
